      <title>国航斥资110亿美元购买100架国产C919飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/air-china-to-buy-100-locally-made-c919-jets-in-11-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国航将购买 100 架中国商飞 C919 喷气式飞机，根据标价计算，这笔交易价值 108 亿美元，这将增强这家本土挑战者对空中客车公司和波音公司的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/air-china-to-buy-100-locally-made-c919-jets-in-11-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 12:16:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
